==Tailoring==
Honey is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[File:Simple Dress.png|36px]] [[Tailoring#Pants|Simple Dress]]. It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
One Honey (of any type) may be requested by several fish in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].

==Tips==
It may prove advantageous to have only one slot free in inventory before gathering honey. The gathered honey will fill up the last inventory slot, preventing the accidental picking of flowers used to make flower honey.  

